:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::
Installation:
*Unzip the file at desired location.
*Use "npm install" command from cmd to install dependencies
*In app.js, set mongo database path.

:::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::::

How to run:
*Run mongod.
*Start the app using "node app.js"

